@node satobjects "Earth-orbiting satellites"
For information on interplanetary spacecraft, click @{"here" link spacecraft.guide/main}.

@remark beginverbatim
 Earth-orbiting satellites
 -------------------------
 Though there are literally thousands of satellites in orbit around the Earth,
descriptions of only a few hundred are provided with "The Digital Universe".
Most of the objects presented here are reasonably well-suited for visual or
binocular observation.

